yingyinNormal.en: Blair said they told you the original party had fallen through so that they could surprise you with a better one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 布莱尔说她们告诉你了原来的那个派对泡汤了，所以她们要在这里给你个惊喜。

yingyinNormal.en: What if you never come up with your original idea?
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你永远都想不出你的原创理论怎么办？

yingyinNormal.en: Original tan, original tile, original too. What do you think, Oleg? Nice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 新色调，新地砖，都是新的，怎么样 Oleg? 不错。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you know the original purpose of the appendix, Leonard? No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道阑尾原本的作用是什么吗，莱纳德？不知道。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, we kept the original data. You can still publish the actual results.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听者，我们保存了原始数据，你还是可以发表你的结果。

yingyinNormal.en: That wasn't a part of our original agreement, and I don't agree to it now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 原始协议内不包含这条，所以我不同意。

yingyinNormal.en: I need to look through to the governing dynamics. Find a truly original idea.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我需要看透管理动力学。找的真正的原创想法。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, wait a minute it's not gonna be Baby Girl? I thought that was so original.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等一下，她不是叫女孩吗？我觉得那个名字很有创意。

yingyinNormal.en: And we can transform an original $10 million investment into billions of dollars.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们可以把原始的1000万美元投资变成几亿美元。

yingyinNormal.en: And you've heard both songs at issue here, the original rap song and Rowby's song?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你听过我们争议的两首歌吗？就是原版说唱和罗比的歌。

yingyinNormal.en: Ms. What was our struggle for? And not just any "Ms. Pac-man," but an original 1982 fully reconditioned podium-style unit, with original coin return. They're even throwing in the stool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是女士，刚刚纠正你多久了？不是普通的“吃豆女士游戏机”而是1982年原装修复的矮款，带有原始的退币口，他们还送了凳子呢。

yingyinNormal.en: What is this? Oh, careful. That's my original series Battlestar Galactica flight suit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是什么？小心，那个是原版太空堡垒卡拉狄加的飞行服。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm still searching, sir, for my… Your original idea, I know. Governing dynamics, sir.
yingyinNormal.zh: 教授，我任在寻找我的… 原创理论，我知道。管理动力学。

yingyinNormal.en: No. But there is an original final draft Ghostbusters script with actual slime stains!
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有，不过有《捉鬼敢死队》的原版终稿，上面真的有黏液的污迹哎。

yingyinNormal.en: We tried to keep it as close to the original as possible. We salvaged as much as we could.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们尽量维持它的原貌，尽全力抢救了。

yingyinNormal.en: You ever heard of a man named Arnold? You could say he was the original settler of these parts.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你听说过一个叫阿诺德的人吗？他算是最早在这些地方定居的人。

yingyinNormal.en: $300 and I'll throw in my original 1979 Mattel millennium falcon with real light speed sound effects.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我付300，我要打造最初的1973年的星战飞船，并使之兼具真正的光速和声效。

yingyinNormal.en: The original weapon was absurdly large. Plenty of steel for two swords. Well, thank you. It's glorious.
yingyinNormal.zh: 原剑大得荒唐，足够重铸两柄。谢谢您，真是一柄好剑。

yingyinNormal.en: A bloomer is one of those original breads that I first learnt how to make when I was about 13 years old.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大圆面包是我13岁时刚开始学做面包时的一种传统的面包。

yingyinNormal.en: You told me that. You didn't tell me your name as a man. John. Which is not terribly original, by the way.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说的，但你没说男性名字，约翰，当然这个名字也不独特。
